613
00:32:55.550 --> 00:32:56.551
Dr. Houseman!

614
00:32:57.251 --> 00:32:58.453
Hang on!

615
00:33:06.327 --> 00:33:07.796
He's right there.
He's right there.

616
00:33:08.664 --> 00:33:09.865
Hang on!

