726
00:39:30.987 --> 00:39:34.825
<i>I am thinking about our son.</i>

727
00:39:42.033 --> 00:39:43.267
Where is he?

728
00:39:44.301 --> 00:39:45.736
Uh, jail.

729
00:39:47.872 --> 00:39:49.840
