1359
01:16:22.012 --> 01:16:23.446
But it's too far away.

1360
01:16:23.480 --> 01:16:24.514
It won't work.

1361
01:16:34.457 --> 01:16:36.893
It's headed our way.

1362
01:16:36.926 --> 01:16:38.795
Bri...

1363
01:16:46.169 --> 01:16:47.971
- It's not stopping!
