1407
01:19:21.561 --> 01:19:23.262
Radio unit 23.

1408
01:19:23.296 --> 01:19:24.464
Stay here.

1409
01:19:24.497 --> 01:19:26.399
Okay, I just need to get to my house.

1410
01:19:26.432 --> 01:19:28.334
