01:19:39.213 --> 01:19:41.315
I have a right
to defend my property, Tom.

1414
01:19:41.348 --> 01:19:42.616
Karen, that's enough!

1415
01:19:42.649 --> 01:19:45.152
Hey, I'm glad you're okay.

1416
01:19:45.185 --> 01:19:48.555
