1425
01:20:14.081 --> 01:20:15.415
- Sonny!
- Hey, mom.

1426
01:20:16.350 --> 01:20:17.451
Are you okay?

1427
01:20:17.484 --> 01:20:19.219
I'm fine.

1428
01:20:19.253 --> 01:20:21.489
