01:21:08.805 --> 01:21:11.140
He's at a military compound
a few hours north.

1451
01:21:11.173 --> 01:21:12.474
A few hours, huh?

1452
01:21:12.508 --> 01:21:14.410
Yeah, we're not gonna make it in time.

1453
01:21:14.443 --> 01:21:15.745
I have an idea.

